title: Self Esteem (Mikal Cronin Feat. Kim Gordon) – “War / Golden God (Demo Recording)”
text: Another day, another track from the anti-Trump charity campaign Our First 100 Days -- and a big one, too! This one comes from Self Esteem, the pairing of Cali garage-pop auteur Mikal Cronin and Sonic Youth icon Kim Gordon. They've joined forces on a demo called "War / Golden God," which is actually two songs: … More »
